{"type":"click","text":"1\n    Color-top Cards — 3열, 깔끔\n  \n  \n    Three Portals\n    \n      \n        \n        \n          Hospital\n          \"We just need a doctor for our surgery.\"\n          One page, mobile-first. Request, check status, done.\n        \n      \n      \n        \n        \n          Admin\n          \"Phone, spreadsheet, check availability, call back.\"\n          20+ assignments a day from one screen. AI for the routine ones.\n        \n      \n      \n        \n        \n          Doctor\n          \"Where do I go, and how much am I making?\"\n          Today's cases with directions. Earnings at a glance. Block days in one tap.\n        \n      \n    \n    I worked alongside the people running this. Designed every animation to get each user to their answer faster. Nothing moves without a reason.","choice":"1","id":null,"timestamp":1774040928606}
